PACKAGE INFO
Textmate Bundle for OpenERP Python files
Snippets are meant to be used with Openerp 5 or later

OpenerpPy has been made to make your life simpler when developing osv models, wizards, etc.

INSTALLATION
Just copy this directory into your ~/Library/Application\ Support/TextMate/Bundles/ directory, and reload bundles. That's it!

You'll see a new bundle named Python Openerp among others!
